at TouchSync's synchronization\nerrors are below 3 and 7 milliseconds on the same wearer and between two\nwearers 10 kilometers apart, respectively.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 25 Sep 2017 03:01:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-09-26"}
