 10%, and when Mars' first prolonged atmospheric\ncollapse occurs for atmospheric pressure > 1 bar.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 25 Sep 2017 03:25:14 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 5 Dec 2019 23:16:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-12-09"}
