tion, velocity, mass and the distance to the Solar System of the MBH can be\nconstrained about $\\sim10\\mu$as, $\\sim1\\mu$as$/$yr, $\\sim 10 M_\\odot$ and\n$\\sim1$pc, respectively.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 25 Sep 2017 06:40:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-02-04"}
