ow for CMB\nobservation and will be one of the major sites in the world along with\nAntarctic and Atacama.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 25 Sep 2017 15:47:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 27 Nov 2017 13:58:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-11-28"}
